						<div class="postbody">You don't need any complex logic for that. With just a few bitwise operations you can detect all kinds of keypresses. Read <a href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/viewtopic.php?p=62142#62142" class="postlink">this post</a> and the ones after it.</div>

